OL,3,CFinnish airline starts weighing
OL,4,Cpassengers before departure
OL,6,FFinnair has started weighing
OL,7,Fpassengers at the departure gate to
OL,8,Frefine its weight estimates for planes
OL,9,Fbefore take-off.
OL,11,FTravellers who volunteer to be
OL,12,Fmeasured by the Finnish airline are
OL,13,Fweighed along with their carry-on
OL,14,Fluggage.
OL,16,FIt isn't all bad news for anybody
OL,17,Ftrying to sneak on items over their
OL,18,Fbaggage limit, as all of the
OL,19,Finformation is anonymised and
OL,20,Faggregated, and won't be used to
OL,21,Fpenalise anybody.
