OL,3,CFinnish airline starts weighing
OL,4,Cpassengers before departure
OL,6,FIn the first full three days of the
OL,7,Ftrial, which started on Monday, 800
OL,8,Fvolunteers had agreed to be weighed,
OL,9,Fwhich "positively surprised" the
OL,10,Fairline.
OL,12,FThe data is being collected "for the
OL,13,Fpurpose of and performance
OL,14,Fcalculations that are needed for the
OL,15,Fsafe operation of flights," Paivyt
OL,16,FTallqvist, Finnair's senior vice
OL,17,Fpresident of communications, told CNN.
