OL,3,CFinnish airline starts weighing
OL,4,Cpassengers before departure
OL,6,FOnly the member of staff at the gate
OL,7,Fwill see the weight, Ms Tallqvist
OL,8,Fadded. Finnair plans to weigh 1,200
OL,9,Fpassengers for the winter season, and
OL,10,Fmore for the summer.
OL,12,FAirlines calculate how heavy a plane
OL,13,Fwill be, including people, , cargo and
OL,14,Fonboard catering, before each take-off.
OL,16,FThe information is paired with the
OL,17,Fplane's centre of gravity, and is used
OL,18,Fto contribute towards a safe departure.
